divs: Sighting DetailsWas outside this evening talking to some neighbors. I looked up into the sky and saw two objects that appeared to be large stars. One was following the other as they traveled NW at a moderate speed. Several of us witnessed the event. At first I thought they might be satellites, but they seemed to be too low, and moving in a slight curve.
